{
  "page": "Feature quote/121",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>“Justice. I remember justice. It had a pleasant taste. Justice was what we were about when <a href=\"/index.php/Beric_Dondarrion\" title=\"Beric Dondarrion\">Beric</a> led us, or so we told ourselves. We were king’s men, knights, and heroes... but some knights are dark and full of terrors, my lady. War makes monsters of us all.” —<a href=\"/index.php/Thoros_of_Myr\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Thoros of Myr\">Thoros of Myr</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_42\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 42\">Chapter 42</a>, Brienne VIII.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403124805\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.006 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.007 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 71/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8414/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 315/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 22/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 528/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    3.682      1 -total\n100.00%    3.682      1 Template:Ref\n 66.60%    2.452      1 Template:Ref/core\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:10808-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403124